<component id="ID_s1_txt15">
<text><![CDATA[1. <textformat blockindent='14'>Alice and Bob agree to use the same two numbers. For example, the base <font color='#006600'><b>number g = 5</b></font> and <font color='#0101BA'><b>prime number p = 23</b></font></textformat><br/><br/>2. <textformat blockindent='14'>Alice generates a <font color='#749103'><b>secret number Xa = 6</b></font>. Bob generates a <font color='#749103'><b>secret number Xb =15</b></font></textformat><br/><br/>3. <textformat blockindent='14'>Alice performs the DH algorithm: <b>g^Xa modulo p = Ya</b>;<br/><font color='#006600'><b>g</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^Xa</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>p</b></font> = (<font color='#006600'><b>5</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^6</b></font> modulo 23) = <font color='#853D93'><b>8 = Ya</b></font>. This value is sent to Bob.</textformat>]]></text>
</component>

