<component id="ID_s2_txt19">
<text><![CDATA[4. <textformat blockindent='14'>Bob performs the DH algorithm:<br/><font color='#006600'><b>g</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^x</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>p</b></font> = (<font color='#006600'><b>5</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^15</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>23</b></font>) = <font color='#996600'><b>19 (Yb)</b></font>. This new number is sent to Alice.</textformat><br/><br/>5. <textformat blockindent='14'>Alice computes a new DH algorithm: <b>Yb^Xa modulo p = Z</b>;<br/><font color='#996600'><b>Y</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^x</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>p</b></font> = (<font color='#996600'><b>19</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^6</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>23</b></font>) = <font color='#FF0000'><b>2</b></font>.</textformat><br/><br/>6. <textformat blockindent='14'>Bob computes a new DH algorithm: <b>Ya^Xb modulo p = Z;</b><br/><font color='#853D93'><b>Y</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^x</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>p</b></font> = (<font color='#853D93'><b>8</b></font><font color='#749103'><b>^15</b></font> modulo <font color='#0101BA'><b>23</b></font>) = <font color='#FF0000'><b>2</b></font>.</textformat>]]></text>
